text: Physick may refer to: *An archaic term for a laxative, or for the practice of medicine generally, in pre-modern medicine *Emlen Physick Estate, Victorian house museum in Cape May, New Jersey, located at 1048 Washington Street *Hill- Keith-Physick House in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, was a home of Philip Syng Physick *Philip Syng Physick (1768–1837), American physician born in Philadelphia, called "father of American surgery" *The Physick Book of Deliverance Dane, the first novel written by Katherine Howe
title: Physick
